data.text:
Took care of business on Senior Day 😤

#LetsRide https://t.co/FLkv4WXVJW

We got the W for our SENIORS ✅

#LetsRide https://t.co/YKUzwysH7A

RT @MACSports: The Broncos end with a dub at Waldo!🐎

@WMU_Football | #MACtion https://t.co/8wpfzuANtM

Sending out the seniors with a victory in their final game at Waldo!!

#BroncosReign | #LetsRide https://t.co/mhHHP4JEct

BRONCOS WIN!!! Western Michigan closes out the regular season with a win over Toledo!

#LetsRide | #BroncosReign https://t.co/FjAtY16JfS
Ryan Selig forces an errant pass and WMU will take over on downs with 1:43 to go!
After review, the ball is moved back to the 29, bringing up 4th and 1 for the Rockets!
The spot is under review on this one
The Rockets move the chains on 3rd down with 1:51 to play
A pair of incomplete passes bring up 3rd and 10 for Toledo
Touchback. 1st and 10 Toledo at the 20 with 2:28 left. Broncos still leading 20-14
WMU is stopped on 3rd down and will punt
No gain on 2nd down. The Rockets use their final timeout with 3:18 on the clock
Zahir Abdus-Salaam runs for four on 1st down. Timeout Rockets with 3:22 to play

PICKED OFF!!! Bricen Garner snares it off of the deflection to give the ball back to WMU at the Toledo 42 with 3:27 to play!

#LetsRide https://t.co/WnyClknEpV
The Broncos punt and Toledo takes over at its 35 with 3:35 to play
Touchdown Rockets. WMU's lead is cut to 20-14 with 5:11 left in the fourth.
Toledo moves into Bronco territory at the 38
WMU punts and it's downed at the Toledo 5
The Broncos take over on downs! 1st and 10 at the Toledo 40
Western Michigan gets another stop on 3rd down! 4th and 1 upcoming for Toledo
A deep shot is broken up by Dorian Jackson! 2nd and 10 Toledo
The Broncos are forced to kick it away. 1st down Rockets from their 31 with 9:19 left
Zaire Barnes swats the 4th down pass down and Western Michigan will take over on downs with 11:09 to play!
Western Michigan gets a stop in the backfield on 3rd and short! 4th and 3 for the Rockets at the WMU 27
Toledo moves inside the WMU 35

The Broncos head into the final quarter with a 13-point advantage!!

#LetsRide https://t.co/UTmnamFPa7
Following a Toledo punt, WMU begins the drive at its own 35. Just over a minute to play in the 3rd

RT @MACSports: Tyler takes this one 63 yards to the residence!🏠💨

@WMU_Football | #MACtion https://t.co/ggRAJ5l7HO
The WMU defense forces another three and out!
Toledo takes over at its 25 following the kickoff

Western Michigan tacks on three! Palmer Domschke hits from 38 yards out to extend the Bronco lead to 20-7!

#LetsRide https://t.co/SxoZjwiXiS

Sean Tyler has just gone over 1,000 yards for the season! He is the 7th Bronco in program history to have a pair of 1,000 yard seasons!!

#LetsRide https://t.co/XCb53qHo6O
WMU gets its offense back out there at the 42

SACK!!! Carter and Fiske meet at the quarterback to force a Toledo punt!

#LetsRide https://t.co/slGELx05bU
The Broncos start the drive with a TFL by Warren Dabney. 2nd and long
WMU is forced to punt, and Toledo will take over from its 20 after a touchback
Following the punt, 1st and 10 Western Michigan at its own 44
The Bronco defense forces a 3 and out!
Toledo takes over at its 25 after a touchback

TOUCHDOWN BRONCOS!!! Sean Tyler takes it to the house from 63 yards out!

#LetsRide https://t.co/1mygFBuMAh
FUMBLE!!! Andre Carter punches it out and Zaire Barnes picks it up for the Broncos! 1st and 10 WMU at the 31!
Toledo has moved into Western Michigan territory
1st and 10 Toledo at its own 30
WMU is forced to punt it away after an incomplete pass on 3rd down
Following the punt, Western Michigan takes over 1st and 10 at its 25
Pressure from Andre Carter forces an incomplete pass on 3rd down and the Rockets will kick it away
Toledo gets the ball at its 25 to start the second half

Western Michigan takes the lead into the locker room!

#LetsRide https://t.co/E3EKwH0lWT

Palmer Domschke hits from 33 yards out to put the Broncos ahead heading into the break!

#LetsRide https://t.co/fqL91NvqGQ
WMU takes a timeout with 2 seconds left to attempt a field goal before the half
Timeout Broncos with 27 seconds left. 2nd and 9 coming up at the Rocket 18
Salopek keeps it on the draw play and moves it into the red zone!
Salopek finds Crooms for a 1st down at the Toledo 33!
Western Michigan takes over at the Toledo 49 with 1:03 remaining in the half
The Bronco defense forces a three and out!
WMU punts and Toledo takes over at its own 8
Timeout Toledo with 2:16 to go. The Broncos will have a 3rd and 7 at the Rocket 42
A short punt gives the Broncos the ball at the Toledo 45 with 2:28 left until the break
